      "comment": "EAGLES FIRST LOVE (8) impressed first-up then took on a much better race last time when fifth over 320m at Listed level at Louisiana Downs (Dirt). Well placed to make amends. CM DASHING CARTEL (10) stuck on well when resuming last start to finish third over 366m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt) after showing good early speed. Has the talent to go a couple better. AJ BIG CASH (2) displayed plenty of early toe over 201m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt) last time and dug deep to score by 0.3 lengths. Finds a suitable race and can run another big race. EYES SO GRAY (1) last appeared when successful by 0.3 lengths over 229m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt) three-and-a-half months ago, the only time she went to the races last prep. Has good early toe so she should be handy in the run. One of the better hopes.",
